    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "二大太监",
        "大太监甲",
        "妲己",
        "纣王",
        "闻仲"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二大太监同上，同打扫。〖小吹打〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二大太监",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四小太监、二宫娥、纣王、妲己同上。吹打完。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梓童随孤来呀，哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（纣王入帐子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "妲己",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回避了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二大太监、四小太监、二宫娥自两边分下。起更鼓。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闻仲 （内二黄导板） 最可叹为国家身遭大难，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖急急风〗。四上手、四鬼卒、二马童、闻仲同上，同斜椅。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闻仲 （回龙） 我的命丧至在绝龙岭前。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（闻仲上椅子，归正。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闻仲 （唢呐二黄正板）半空中云磨响霹雳闪电，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一口气吹散了云雾归天。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到如今只落得孤身回还。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恶狠狠三只眼杀气冲天。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我背后身插着打将神鞭。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二冲头，打堂鼓。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仲",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "站至在金阶上且把话言："
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仲",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "寿仙宫请我主驾出金銮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我本是老闻仲西歧回转"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "二黄导板",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "龙床上只听得有人呼唤，"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "二黄导板",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我本是老闻仲西歧回转"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "梦见了朝歌城塌了半边。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我本是老闻仲西歧回转"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我本是老闻仲西歧回转"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "只觉得阴风吹体似冰寒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我本是老闻仲西歧回转"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闻仲 （回龙） 我的主休惊怕细听根源："
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（唢呐二黄正板）臣本是老闻仲西歧回转，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "魂灵儿进朝歌面见龙颜。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怒恼了众弟子会战阵前："
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李哪吒手使相乾坤神圈；"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "邓蝉玉五色石无人敢拦；"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "龙须虎发飞石重如泰山。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "全仗着定海珠蛟龙神鞭。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他请来燃灯道下了高山。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "惹恼了三教主下了凡间。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将为臣围至在绝龙岭前。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "九龙罩罩为臣化为灰烟。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎能舍我主爷锦绣江山？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "最可叹锦江山六百余年。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣本当与我主——"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "再诉一遍，"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "怕只怕五更尽难去归天。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四上手、四鬼卒、二马童同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仲",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "周室兴商汤灭就在眼前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（闻仲下。天亮。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "二黄导板",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "时才间听闻仲细说一遍，"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "醒来时不由我胆战心寒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（妲己醒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "妲己",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁为何这般模样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，梓童有所不知：昨夜三更，偶得一兆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妲己",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不知主公得何龙兆？"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梦见太师闻仲，回转朝歌。他言到命丧西歧，因此心惊胆怕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妲己",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启奏万岁：倘若有不测，妾妃自能领兵，剿灭西歧。我主但放宽心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此说来，全仗梓童你了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "这江山有梓童定无凶险，"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "哪管那西伯侯出兵歧山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "但愿你怀龙胎生下儿男。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梓童随寡人来呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "纣王",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（纣王、妲己同下。）"
        }
      ],
